WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.030
Good morning, family, or good evening or

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:05.230
wherever you are. Thank you for joining

00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:07.350
me again tonight. We're going to pray,

00:00:07.360 --> 00:00:09.150
but I want to go over what the Lord

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:13.790
showed us yesterday in prayer.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:15.870
I haven't had

00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:21.310
an experience like that ever on a live.

00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:23.830
You know, I have dreams, I have

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:26.110
visions, that the Lord shows me quite a

00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:27.510
few things,

00:00:27.520 --> 00:00:30.750
but never like that where

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:32.710
when I'm praying,

00:00:32.720 --> 00:00:34.710
I feel like I'm

00:00:34.720 --> 00:00:36.190
leaving.

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:38.710
And last night,

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:40.550
that's why I told

00:00:40.550 --> 00:00:40.560
Diana,

00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:42.830
"Pray for me. Lay your hand on

00:00:42.830 --> 00:00:42.840
me,"because

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:44.790
it brings me back into reality a

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:47.550
little bit. It snaps.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:49.510
When I go into the spirit like that,

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.190
I'm able to see so far. There

00:00:51.190 --> 00:00:51.200
are

00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:53.430
sometimes when I'm going in, I can see

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:56.350
the years. I can see so

00:00:56.360 --> 00:01:00.110
much detail. I can smell things.

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:02.230
It's heavenly.

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:04.070
But at the same time, when you're in the

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:05.750
natural, it

00:01:05.760 --> 00:01:07.630
has a tendency to freak your

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:09.230
flesh out a little bit is what I want to

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:10.310
tell you.

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:12.470
I don't know how else to describe it

00:01:12.470 --> 00:01:12.480
than

00:01:12.480 --> 00:01:16.030
it makes your flesh—because the

00:01:16.040 --> 00:01:17.830
spirit is more real to me than the

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:20.390
natural body.

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:23.870
Our spirit realm is

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:26.550
more real than the natural realm.

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:29.110
And people, if you learn to tap into

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:31.390
it and get in with the Holy Spirit and

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:32.345
walk with him,

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:34.350
he'll show you the things to come.

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:37.110
But I'm telling you, the other

00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:39.950
side is just as real and more real

00:01:39.960 --> 00:01:42.550
than this realm.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:44.510
And when you start to get over and

00:01:44.520 --> 00:01:47.070
look over and see what God is

00:01:47.080 --> 00:01:48.470
doing,

00:01:48.480 --> 00:01:50.470
it's beautiful

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:52.950
and you go, "Wow."You know, I long for

00:01:52.960 --> 00:01:55.710
the day Jesus Christ comes and gets us.

00:01:55.720 --> 00:01:57.270
But I'm going to go over because a lot of

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:59.110
people go, "Brandon, you okay?

00:01:59.110 --> 00:01:59.120
What's

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:01.030
that all

00:02:01.030 --> 00:02:01.040
about?"Well,

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:04.310
to try to explain the supernatural

00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:07.270
in some things is like trying to

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:10.430
explain a hot sandy beach to

00:02:10.440 --> 00:02:11.910
an Eskimo.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:14.150
You don't. It's

00:02:14.150 --> 00:02:14.160
real hard

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:17.110
because the Eskimo has no

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:19.670
idea what it's like to feel the tropics.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:22.350
He's only used to igloos and

00:02:22.360 --> 00:02:23.436
cold weather.

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:28.990
So,

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:29.710
where do I start?

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:36.230
I saw 2027. I saw the storm, but I

00:02:36.240 --> 00:02:40.030
saw the prophet, Kim Clement,

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:43.710
and he was interceding for America,

00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:46.670
but he was playing on the

00:02:46.680 --> 00:02:49.510
other side. It

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:53.630
was glorious, but he looked so young.

00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:56.790
I told

00:02:56.790 --> 00:02:56.800
Donna

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:59.110
through a text earlier

00:02:59.120 --> 00:03:01.590
his skin looked like he had Botox. His

00:03:01.600 --> 00:03:03.590
skin had no wrinkles. He

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:03.600
looked

00:03:03.600 --> 00:03:05.750
so fresh and clean. His

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:07.630
shirt was red and he

00:03:07.630 --> 00:03:07.640
looked

00:03:07.640 --> 00:03:10.990
so pressed and like a

00:03:10.990 --> 00:03:11.000
dry-cleaned

00:03:11.000 --> 00:03:12.830
shirt. Everything looked

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:15.710
so perfect. His hair was perfect and

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:17.550
long just like it always was when he was

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:20.790
on the earth. But he was playing a

00:03:20.790 --> 00:03:20.800
keyboard

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:22.990
that was like a

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.990
plastic keyboard like we have here like

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:28.350
a Yamaha or whatever,

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:31.430
like a nice keyboard, but he was playing

00:03:31.440 --> 00:03:34.470
that keyboard and he was interceding

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:36.990
and praying for America.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:38.590
But remember, do you all remember

00:03:38.600 --> 00:03:40.430
whenever I had the vision of

00:03:40.430 --> 00:03:40.440
Lynn

00:03:40.440 --> 00:03:42.830
Hammond's sister Lucy and

00:03:44.360 --> 00:03:46.350
Rachel Tefatiller

00:03:46.350 --> 00:03:46.360
and Jeannie

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:47.790
Wilkerson and they were

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:49.070
sitting on the quilt and all that and it

00:03:49.080 --> 00:03:51.390
was the glorious time that I saw that

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:52.710
they were praying, interceding with

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:54.270
brother

00:03:54.270 --> 00:03:54.280
Halverson?

00:03:54.280 --> 00:03:57.190
This was similar to that.

00:03:57.200 --> 00:04:00.230
But as he was praying,

00:04:00.240 --> 00:04:04.390
there was this huge cloud

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:05.910
behind him

00:04:05.920 --> 00:04:08.390
with lightning that was going around

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:10.950
him and he was prophesying, but I

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:12.670
couldn't make out what he was saying. He

00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:13.990
was

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:16.069
declaring and he was speaking over

00:04:16.079 --> 00:04:18.990
America.

00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:22.630
And as he was playing his keyboard,

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:25.070
you could feel the glory. I was watching

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:27.190
him, but he was not moved by what was

00:04:27.200 --> 00:04:30.270
around him. He was focused on the task

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:33.910
at hand in his heavenly body.

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:36.110
And I thought,

00:04:36.120 --> 00:04:39.550
"What in the world am I

00:04:39.550 --> 00:04:39.560
seeing?"But

00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:42.710
I was looking and I saw 2027,

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:46.190
2028.

00:04:46.200 --> 00:04:50.150
And I asked Donna, I said,

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:51.950
"Did your dad say anything about

00:04:51.950 --> 00:04:51.960
2027?"and

00:04:51.960 --> 00:04:54.030
she sent me the video and

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:55.910
I've been watching it since she sent it

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:58.110
and the anointing on this clip is

00:04:58.120 --> 00:05:00.350
amazing as he's playing.

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:03.030
But it wasn't about 2028,

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:05.350
but I thought it was interesting

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:08.230
as I was interceding and we were praying

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:10.430
for our nation.

00:05:10.440 --> 00:05:13.150
The Lord showed us so much, but I

00:05:13.160 --> 00:05:14.870
want to get to what the Lord showed me

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:16.070
today

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:17.950
as I was driving around. I went out and I

00:05:17.960 --> 00:05:21.510
was

00:05:21.510 --> 00:05:21.520
getting—you

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:23.830
know, I like to

00:05:23.840 --> 00:05:25.950
feed the deer in our neighborhood. The

00:05:25.960 --> 00:05:28.070
deer like to come and

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:30.590
eat the corn.

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:32.990
So I put corn out and things for them

00:05:32.990 --> 00:05:33.000
because

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.590
I like to get them to come up close

00:05:34.600 --> 00:05:35.870
to the house

00:05:35.870 --> 00:05:35.880
because

00:05:35.880 --> 00:05:38.550
I like to watch them.

00:05:38.560 --> 00:05:40.390
And the Lord spoke to me and he

00:05:40.400 --> 00:05:42.430
started talking to me about the Supreme

00:05:42.440 --> 00:05:44.430
Court justices.

00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:46.030
And he said to me, "Brandon, I

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:47.630
told you

00:05:47.640 --> 00:05:49.910
I was giving this nation a window of

00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:51.310
opportunity

00:05:51.320 --> 00:05:55.870
for a great wealth transfer.

00:05:55.880 --> 00:06:00.270
You pray into their decision

00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:02.870
concerning the tariffs

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:05.670
and the finances of

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:09.510
America."And

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:10.670
I said, "Lord, what happens if it

00:06:10.670 --> 00:06:10.680
doesn't

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:12.510
come to pass? What

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:14.790
am I looking

00:06:14.790 --> 00:06:14.800
at?"He

00:06:14.800 --> 00:06:17.630
was so stern with me. He

00:06:17.640 --> 00:06:21.110
said, "It will come to pass. You speak

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:23.430
into it.

00:06:23.440 --> 00:06:25.310
There are no ifs and buts about it

00:06:25.320 --> 00:06:27.710
in the spirit realm with me. You say to

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:31.270
the mountain, 'Be removed.'We will as a

00:06:31.280 --> 00:06:35.870
nation have revival. We will as a nation

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:37.950
have a

00:06:37.960 --> 00:06:41.310
wave of the finances for the

00:06:41.320 --> 00:06:43.910
outpouring of the glorious church to

00:06:43.920 --> 00:06:46.470
fund this gospel and get it promoted

00:06:46.480 --> 00:06:47.990
around the world.

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:51.470
We will be victorious."He said, "You

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:53.950
speak to it.

00:06:53.960 --> 00:06:57.670
There is no plan B.

00:06:57.680 --> 00:07:00.990
You speak to it."He rebuked me for

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:02.350
having

00:07:02.360 --> 00:07:04.230
a mealy mouth, you know, like, "Oh

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:06.230
Lord, what happens if it doesn't

00:07:06.230 --> 00:07:06.240
happen?"He

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:08.870
said,

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:12.294
"You speak."He corrected me.

00:07:12.880 --> 00:07:17.270
And he said, "America must—you must,

00:07:17.270 --> 00:07:17.280
Brandon—this

00:07:17.280 --> 00:07:20.350
must take place

00:07:20.360 --> 00:07:23.990
for the glorious outpouring for a window

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:26.350
of opportunity."And I'm not trying to

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:27.910
yell. It's just when the anointing

00:07:27.920 --> 00:07:29.830
starts coming on me, you have to deal

00:07:29.840 --> 00:07:31.910
with it. Turn your volume down.

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.350
I

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:35.750
just get tired of all of

00:07:35.750 --> 00:07:35.760
it.

00:07:35.760 --> 00:07:39.270
This is what he said to me:

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:41.950
"I saw the wave. I

00:07:41.960 --> 00:07:44.350
told you you would have a wave.

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:47.310
It will be a short-lived wave and there

00:07:47.320 --> 00:07:49.310
will be gold on

00:07:49.310 --> 00:07:49.320
them."He

00:07:49.320 --> 00:07:52.070
said, "Fill your pockets,

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:55.270
for a great storm is coming,

00:07:55.280 --> 00:07:57.470
but I will always provide for my

00:07:57.480 --> 00:07:59.670
beloved

00:07:59.670 --> 00:07:59.680
Brandon."There

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:02.510
is a storm coming, church, but

00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:05.230
it's not yet.

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:07.070
He said, "Pray for Donald Trump,

00:08:07.080 --> 00:08:08.910
Brandon.

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:13.070
I'm using him for this

00:08:13.070 --> 00:08:13.080
season."And

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:18.430
the enemy would want him removed.

00:08:18.440 --> 00:08:21.870
His life is in danger. You must pray for

00:08:21.880 --> 00:08:23.630
him.

00:08:23.640 --> 00:08:26.070
The enemy doesn't want him to

00:08:26.080 --> 00:08:28.310
live long and finish

00:08:28.320 --> 00:08:30.510
strong, to finish his assignment on the

00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:33.709
earth. And he's not done yet.

00:08:33.719 --> 00:08:36.110
And the Lord strictly told me

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:37.790
today when I was out doing what I was

00:08:37.800 --> 00:08:40.190
doing, "Brandon,

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:42.670
you need to intercede for him. It's the

00:08:42.680 --> 00:08:44.710
church's

00:08:44.710 --> 00:08:44.720
responsibility."And

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:48.230
I saw a financial outpouring still

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:50.030
concerning

00:08:50.040 --> 00:08:53.310
certain metals

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:55.630
and cryptos,

00:08:55.640 --> 00:08:57.750
concerning certain

00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:01.350
foreign currencies.

00:09:01.360 --> 00:09:03.230
Like I said, I'm not a financial

00:09:03.230 --> 00:09:03.240
adviser.

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:04.910
I cannot come on here and

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:06.510
tell the body of Christ what to do because

00:09:06.520 --> 00:09:09.670
I can miss it just like

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:11.710
anybody else can. I'm human.

00:09:11.720 --> 00:09:14.430
And I want to tell you when you see in

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:16.310
part and hear in part,

00:09:18.280 --> 00:09:20.110
we're all works in progress. I

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:22.190
want to tell you that, but when it comes

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:23.590
to this, you need to pray about it for

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:25.430
your own family and what God is telling

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:28.230
you to do. It's not my job.

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:30.870
So I want you to intercede for

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:32.230
these things because the Lord said to me,

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:34.710
"This is part of the outpouring.

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:37.190
The wealth

00:09:37.200 --> 00:09:40.150
transfer is part of the

00:09:40.150 --> 00:09:40.160
end-time

00:09:40.160 --> 00:09:41.630
harvest. Do you

00:09:41.640 --> 00:09:43.310
understand? And I'm giving you a

00:09:43.310 --> 00:09:43.320
window."And

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:44.870
he said, "Brandon, you're

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:47.230
already one year into that

00:09:49.710 --> 00:09:49.720
window."And

00:09:51.640 --> 00:09:54.150
he said, "What will you do with the

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:57.356
time that I have given

00:09:57.366 --> 00:09:57.910
you?"for

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.470
an hourglass was filled up a little

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:01.990
bit more.

00:10:02.000 --> 00:10:04.310
"What will you do with the time? I've

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:07.670
extended the time for the church

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:10.230
for this

00:10:10.230 --> 00:10:10.240
window."And

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:13.350
I saw the wave. I saw the

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:16.270
finances. I saw the blessing. But it's

00:10:16.280 --> 00:10:18.710
all connected. And that's like what I

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:21.430
was hearing today.

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:23.430
The enemy would try to put a kink in the

00:10:23.440 --> 00:10:25.270
hose.

00:10:25.280 --> 00:10:27.670
No more delays.

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:30.510
It's called

00:10:30.520 --> 00:10:33.030
a divine reversal. It's time for the

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:35.830
supernatural divine reversal in your

00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:37.350
finances,

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:39.150
a supernatural blessing on your

00:10:39.160 --> 00:10:40.630
household.

00:10:40.640 --> 00:10:42.430
You see, the enemy is fighting because he

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:44.670
knows his time is short. Just like it

00:10:44.680 --> 00:10:46.910
talks about in Revelation, the

00:10:46.920 --> 00:10:49.990
enemy knows. He knows, he sees. We went

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:52.750
over two videos ago that his time

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:55.110
is short,

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:57.110
but the finances are his wheelhouse.

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:59.590
And that was when we went into the wars

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:01.190
and all the things that he's trying

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:03.430
to do. But the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm

00:11:03.440 --> 00:11:04.750
giving you a window. Do you

00:11:04.760 --> 00:11:06.790
understand? But you have to be a

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:09.110
contender that fights for it. You have

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:11.990
to pray. You have to not have this 'well,

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:14.630
whatever will be, will

00:11:14.630 --> 00:11:14.640
be'attitude."David

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:16.910
didn't have a "whatever will be,

00:11:16.920 --> 00:11:18.590
will be"attitude with the Goliath that was

00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:20.470
standing in front of him.

00:11:20.480 --> 00:11:22.990
You know, "Lord, if you

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:24.950
deliver me, you deliver. If you don't, you

00:11:24.960 --> 00:11:26.870
don't. The giant's pretty

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:28.590
big;

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:30.910
I guess if he takes my

00:11:30.910 --> 00:11:30.920
head..."He

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:32.230
didn't have that. What did he have?

00:11:32.240 --> 00:11:35.230
He had a bulldog faith. He said, "Who is

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:37.910
this that tries to defy the armies

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:39.750
of the living God? This uncircumcised

00:11:39.760 --> 00:11:41.350
Philistine?

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:44.510
Who is this?"But David went after

